                        <head>No. 592.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Cashing</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1875-03-12"><hi rend="italic">March</hi> 12,
                                1875</date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Credentials presented the 10th; ratification signed the 11th, and sent
                            the same day by express.</p>
